parameters: ここで単品アイテム入手

There are demons swarming around the corpse! Could
it be...
We have to drive them away no matter what!
We managed to defeat them, but...

Thank you... I was about to become a demon beast
soon...

Yes, that's right. I was attacked here on my way
back to my hometown, the Village of the Sacred
Tree...
Could it be that your child wasn't with you...?

Yes, unfortunately, this child... their soul had
already safely arrived in the village.

Thanks to you, Kura and I seem to be able to
return to the sanctuary of the Village of the
Sacred Tree just like this...

It seems... it was the souls of a parent and child
who couldn't ascend...
I want to make the earth... safer...
